title: PvP game of SR under 33minutes(Mission)
body:
Hey guys 
This may be a noob question but  my team managed to finish a game at 32minutes(luck) but the mission didnt get done.why? Am I forgeting something (I had the project icon equipped)
thx

replies.body: Straaaaange. 32 Min should have definitely counted. Hit up your EUW game agents in a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so they can double check this and get it fixed if needed!
Okay it has been solved! thank you very much for the help!

I found it strange as well but I didnt know if there was more details to the mission that I didnt know but its difficult to get a SR game under 33 minutes so I kinda wanted to know what was wrong. Thanks for the help! I have already sent a ticket lets see what they say.
